\h 2 Korin 
\toc3 2KO 
\toc2 2 Korin 
\toc1 Pol…®n Ak…®nafarir Namba 2, a Korin…®n Nguibam…®n Itir Sios Baghava an Osiri 
\mt1 Pol…®n Ak…®nafarir Namba 2,  // a Korin…®n Nguibam…®n Itir Sios Baghava an Osiri 
\mt2 O 
\mt1 2 Korin 
\imt1 Akar Faragha Zuim 
\ip Korin…®n nguibar ekiam…®n sios…®n gumazamizir maba akar kurabar Pol m…®keme. Ez…® bizir kam Pol gamima, a bar oseme. Pol Korin…®n sios ko akabar k…®rasa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a me bagha ak…®nafarir kam osiri. Egh ua me gakuegham. 
\ip Ez…® akar otevir ak…®nafarim…®n itir mam, Pol akar gavgavir a faragha Korinba bagha amizim…®n gun m…®gei. An akar kam m…®k…®man aghua, ez…® me a barazir puvat…®gha, akar kurabar a m…®keme. Ez…® kamagh…®n an akar gavgavim me gan…®ngi. Ez…® me an akam baregha uan arazibar k…®ri, kamagh…®n amiz…®, a dat…®r…®gh…®n me bagha guizbang…®ra bar akonge. 
\ip Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Judian Distrigh…®n itir Krais…®n adarasi, me paza iti. Ez…® Pol me bagha dag…®aba akumakumigh, da inigh mang…® me dan…®ngasa. Egha Sapta 8 ko 9, Pol akar Korinba navibagh aghuvk…®nt…®ma, me dag…®aba is…® ingangarir kam dan…®ngamin akabav gei. 
\ip Ez…® ak…®nafarim…®n akar otevir abuananam, aposel…®n ifavarir iza Korin…®n itir maba, me Pol…®n ziam d…®kab…®ra an Aposel…®n ingangarim gas…®ghas…®si. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Pol men arazir kurabar gun m…®gei. 
\c 1  
\ms1 Pol ingangarir God aposelbagh an…®ngizim…®n gun m…®gei 
\mr (Sapta 1--7) 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 1:1 \xt Aposel 18:1; 1 Korin 1:1\x*K…® Pol, k…® Krais Iesus…®n aposel…®n mam. God uan ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua, aposel…®n m…®n ikiasa na am…®sefe. K…® en aveghbuam Timoti ko, ga ak…®nafarir kam osirigha, ia Korin…®n nguibar ekiam…®n aven God…®n sios…®n itiba, ko God…®n gumazamizir Akaian Provins…®n danganiba bar adar itiba, ia bagha an osirigha anemadi.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 1:2 \xt 1 Korin 1:3\x*Egha ga God ko m…®g…®a ghaze, God en Afeziam, ko en Ekiam Krais Iesus ian apangkuv, navir am…®rizim ia dan…®ngam. 
\s1 Pol God an akurazir bizim bagha a m…®naba 
\p  
\v 3 \x - \xo 1:3 \xt Rom 15:5; Efesus 1:3; 1 Pita 1:3\x*E God…®n ziam fam, a God, egha en Ekiam Krais Iesus…®n Afeziam. A en Afeziam, ez…® akurvazir arazim ko apangkuvir arazim an otifi. Ez…® a, gumazamizir os…®mt…®ziba ateriba, men g…®rak…®rang…®n tuiva navir am…®rizim me gan…®di.  
\v 4 God kamagh…®n ifonge, an en g…®rak…®rang…®n tuiva navir am…®rizim e gan…®di mogh…®n, e gumazamizir os…®mt…®zir av…®riba ateritabar g…®rak…®rang…®n tuiva navir am…®rizim me dan…®ngam. Kamagh…®n, os…®mt…®ziba e bativir dughiabar, an en g…®rak…®rang…®n tuiva navir am…®rizim e gan…®di.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 1:5 \xt Onger Akaba 34:19; 94:19; Kolosi 1:24\x*Krais os…®mt…®zir bar ekiam aterez…® mogh…®n e uaghan aneteri. Ez…® God Krais…®n g…®rak…®rang…®n tugha navir am…®rizim a gan…®ngiz…® mogh…®n, God Krais…®n ingangarim…®n, en g…®rak…®rang…®n tuz…®ma navir am…®rizim e giz…®fa.  
\v 6 God kamaghsua, ia navir am…®rizim ko an akurvazim iniam, bizir kam…®n e os…®mt…®zim ateri. God navir am…®rizim e dan…®ng…®va, a uaghan navir am…®rizim ia dan…®ngam. Ia en m…®n tuivigh gavgavigh os…®mt…®ziba atert…®, God navir am…®rizim en m…®n ia dan…®ngam.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 1:7 \xt Rom 8:17; 2 Timoti 2:12\x*Ez…® e kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ikia bar fogha ghaze, ia tuivigh gavgavigham. E fo, ia e ko os…®mt…®zim ateri, kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia uaghan e ko navir am…®rizim iniam. 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 1:8 \xt Aposel 19:23; 1 Korin 15:32\x*Nan adarasi, os…®mt…®zir Esian Provins…®n e batozim, ia a g…®foghasa. Os…®mt…®zir bar ekiam e avaragha, en gavgaviba bar dagh afira. Ez…® kamagh…®n e ghaze, e ti ovegham.  
\v 9 Bar guizbang…®ra, e mati gumazim jas ovengasava a m…®gei mogh…®n, e uari barasi. God kamaghsua, e uan gavgavibara n…®ghn…®ghan kogham. Puvat…®, e God…®n gavgavimra n…®ghn…®gh a gis…®n tugham, a gumazir ovengezibagh amiz…® me ua d…®kafi. Kamagh…®n, bizir kam e bato.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 1:10 \xt 2 Timoti 4:18; 2 Pita 2:9\x*Kar bizir bar kuram, an e gamiz…® e atam oveghai. Ez…® God en akura. Egh a g…®n uam en akuragham. E n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ikia bar fogha ghaze, zurara bizir kuram e bativt…®ma, God uam en akuraght…®ma, e deraghv…®ra ikiam.  
\v 11 Egh ia en akuragh God ko m…®k…®m. Eght…® God gumazamizir av…®ribar d…®mdiaba baragh en akuragham. Eght…® gumazamizir bar av…®riba ganigh, me God en akuragha e gamizir biziba bagh a m…®nabagham. 
\s1 Pol Korinbagh ifarazir puvat…® 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 1:12 \xt 1 Korin 1:17; 2:4; 2:13; 2 Korin 2:17; Hibru 13:18\x*Bizir kam na gamima k…® bar akonge. Nan navir averiam…®n, k…® uan araziba derav…®ra da tuis…®gha kamagh…®n fo, k…® nguazir kam…®n ikia arazir aghuim gami, egha guizbang…®ra ian damazibara e arazir bar aghuim gami. K…® arazir God nan akazir kam gamua God baghav…®ra itir arazibar g…®n ghua, bizitam ian modozir puvat…®. K…® nguazir kam…®n fofozim isa arazir kam gamizir pu. Puvat…®, k…® God…®n apangkuvim…®n gavgavim isa, arazir kam gami.  
\v 13-14 \x - \xo 1:13-14 \xt 2 Korin 5:12; Filipai 2:16\x*Egha k…® ia bagha ak…®nafarim osirava, akar ia derav…®ra gan dar m…®ngaribagh foghamiba, k…® dararama osiri. K…® ia bagha akar igharazitaba osirir puvat…®. Guizbang…®ra, dughiar mabar k…® osirir m…®g…®r…®g…®ar maba, ia deragha dagh fozir puvat…®. K…® kamaghsua, ia en Ekiam Iesus Izamin Dughiam…®n, k…® ia bagha ziar ekiam iniz…® mogh…®n, ia na bagh ziar ekiam iniam. Kamagh…®n ia guizbang…®ra nan akabar m…®ngaribagh foghasa, k…® ifonge. 
\p  
\v 15-16 \x - \xo 1:15-16 \xt Aposel 19:21; 1 Korin 16:5-6\x*K…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikia ghaze, ia na bagh ziar ekiam iniam. Ez…® bizir kam bagha, k…® akam ak…®righa ghaze, k…® faragh iz…® ian ganam. Egh k…® ia ategh, Masedonian Provins…®n mangam. Egha k…® Masedonia Provins ataghizir dughiam…®n, k…® uamategh iz…® ian ganasa n…®ghn…®si. Ez…® arazir kam…®n God dughiar pumuning…®n arazir aghuim…®n ia damuam. Eght…® ia nan akuraght…®, k…® Judian Distrigh…®n mangam.  
\v 17 Ez…® manmagh…®n ami? Ia ti ghaze, k…® amizir m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba, k…® pura ia gifari. Ia ti ghaze, k…® nguazir kam…®n gumazamizibar m…®n puram akar d…®k…®r…®zibagh amua dar ghuangs…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra,‚Äù o ‚ÄúPuvat…®,‚Äù uagharam aning m…®k…®mam? Bar puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 18 God zurara uan m…®g…®r…®g…®abar g…®nt…®si. Ez…® kamagh…®ra k…® guizbang…®ra ia m…®gei, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar k…® ia gamiba bar, da uaghara ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra,‚Äù o ‚ÄúPuvat…®,‚Äù m…®geir pu.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 1:19 \xt Aposel 9:20; 18:5\x*K…®, ko Sailas, ko Timoti, e ian tong…®n God…®n Otarim Krais Iesus…®n akam kuri. Ez…® ia bar fo Krais, ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra,‚Äù ko ‚ÄúPuvat…®,‚Äù uagharam aning…®n m…®geir puvat…®. Krais zurara guizbang…®ra m…®gei.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 1:20 \xt Rom 15:8-9; Akar Mogomem 3:14\x*God…®n akar d…®k…®r…®zir av…®riba iti. Ez…® Krais ‚ÄúGuizbang…®ra,‚Äù akar d…®k…®r…®zir kaba bar dav gei. Kamagh…®n, e God…®n akam barazima a Krais…®n ziam…®n ghaze, ‚ÄúA guizbang…®ra,‚Äù ez…® e God…®n ziam fe.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 1:21 \xt 1 Jon 2:20; 2:27\x*Ez…® God uab…® gavgavim isa, e ko ia gan…®di, ez…® e Krais ko porogha, ikia gavgafi. Egha a uab…® ua bagha e am…®sefe.  
\v 22 \x - \xo 1:22 \xt Rom 8:16-17; 2 Korin 5:5; Efesus 1:13-14; 2 Timoti 2:19; 1 Jon 2:27; Akar Mogomem 2:17\x*Egha a uab…® uan inabazir ababanim e gat…®, kamagh…®n me en gan fogh suam, e an gumazamizibara. Egha uan Duam en navir averiabar ikiasa an e gan…®ngi. God…®n Duamra a uaghan bizir aghuir faragha zuir mam, God e dan…®ngasa. E God…®n Duam inigha g…®vagha, kamagh…®n e fo, e guizbang…®ra bizir av…®rir maba sara iniam. 
\s1 Pol zuam…®ra Korin…®n ghuzir puvat…® 
\p  
\v 23 \x - \xo 1:23 \xt Rom 1:9; 2 Korin 11:31\x*God, a gumazir nan m…®g…®r…®g…®aba gavgavim dagh an…®dim, egha a nan navim…®n gari. Ez…® k…® an ziam…®n guizbang…®ra kamagh…®n m…®gei, k…® os…®mt…®zim ia dan…®ngan aghuagha, kamagh…®n, k…® zuam…®ra Korin…®n izezir puvat…®. A kamagh…®ra tu.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 1:24 \xt 1 Pita 5:3\x*K…® kamagh…®n m…®kemezir puvat…®, e ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgavibar gant…® da en apengan ikiam. Puvat…®. E fo, ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n ikia m…®tivigha gavgavigha g…®fa. Egh e ian agorogem damut…®, an otivasa, ia ko ingari. 
\c 2  
\nb  
\v 1 \x - \xo 2:1 \xt 1 Korin 4:21; 2 Korin 12:21\x*K…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, k…® ia bagh izan kogham, egh ia damut…® ia fom…®ra na basemez…® mogh…®n na bas…®man kogham. Kamagh…®n k…® izezir puvat…®.  
\v 2 Egh k…® ia damut…®, ia na basemeght…®ma, tina ik…® na damut…® k…® bar akuegham? Ia, gumazamizir k…® ia gamiz…® ia na basemeziba, iarara ikiam.  
\v 3 Ia gumazamizir agorogem na gan…®diba, kamagh…®n k…® ia bagh iz…® os…®mt…®zim ia dan…®ngan aghua. Ez…® bizir kam bagha k…® fom…®ra ia bagha ak…®nafarir mam osirigha anemada. K…® fo, k…® bizitam bagh bar akueght…®, ia uaghan bar mogh…®ra bar akuegham.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 2:4 \xt Aposel 20:31\x*Guizbang…®ra, k…® ia bagha ak…®nafarim osirir dughiam…®n, k…® bar ian apangkuvigha, nan navim bar osemez…®, k…® puv…®ram azi. K…® os…®mt…®zim ia dan…®ngasa ak…®nafarir kam osirizir puvat…®. K…® ghaze, ia kamagh…®n fogh suam, k…® bar ia gifuegha, bar uan navim ia gan…®ngi. Kamagh…®n k…® ia bagha osiri. 
\s1 Korinba, gumazir arazir kuram gamizim…®n arazir kuram g…®n amang 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 2:5 \xt 1 Korin 5:1; Galesia 4:12\x*Gumazitam os…®mt…®zim gumazir igharazibagh an…®ngi, an os…®mt…®zim na gan…®ngizir puvat…®. K…® m…®g…®r…®g…®ar gavgavir av…®ribar bizir kam m…®k…®man aghua. K…® kamagh…®n m…®k…®masa, a ia gamiz…®ma, ian naviba bar mogh…®ra, mong ian oseme.  
\v 6 Ez…® ian av…®riba ghaze, gumazir kam a ivezir kuratam inigh. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n an a inigha g…®vagha, kamagh…®ra tu.  
\v 7 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia arazir igharazitam…®n dat…®r…®gh…®n a damu. Ia an arazir kuraba g…®n amadagh…®va, an g…®rak…®rang…®n tugh, navir am…®rizim a dan…®ng. Puvat…®ght…®, os…®mt…®zir bar ekiam gumazir kam d…®kab…®ragham.  
\v 8 Kamagh…®n, k…® ia gakaghora ghaze, ia an akaght…® a fogham, ia a gifuegha mamagh…®ra iti.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 2:9 \xt 2 Korin 7:15; 10:6\x*Ak…®nafarir k…® faragha osirizim, mar k…® pura ia basamasa an osiri. K…® kamagh…®n foghasa, ia nan akabar g…®nt…®gha biziba bar dagh ami, o puvat…®?  
\v 10 Eght…® ia gumazitam…®n arazir kuraba g…®n amang…®t…®, k…® uaghan da g…®n amangam. Eght…® k…® g…®n amangamin arazir kuratam ik…®t…®, k…® ian akurvaghs…® Krais…®n damazim a g…®n amangam.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 2:11 \xt Luk 22:31\x*K…® atiatia ghaze, Satan ti e gifaragh e d…®kab…®ragham. Kamagh…®n k…® arazir kuraba g…®n amadi. E Satan…®n mogomer n…®ghn…®zir kurabagh fogha g…®fa. 
\s1 Pol Taitus…®n ganasa 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 2:12 \xt Aposel 14:27; 1 Korin 16:9\x*\x - \xo 2:12-13 \xt Aposel 20:1\x*K…® Krais…®n Akar Aghuim akunasa izava, Troas…®n nguibar ekiam…®n otogha gari, Ekiam k…® ingangarir kam damuasa, a na bagha tuavim at…®.  
\v 13 Ez…® k…® uan aveghbuam Taitus…®n ganizir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n nan navim derazir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® Troasia ategha uamategha iza Masedonian Provins…®n oto. 
\s1 Aposelba God…®n gavgavim…®n m…®dorozibagh afisi 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® God, Krais ko porogha en faragha zuima, e an g…®n ghua kalabuziar gumazamizibar m…®n ghua bar akuegha m…®g…®a ghaze, Krais modorozim gafiragha apaniba d…®kab…®ragha g…®fa! Ez…® arazir kam…®n gumazamiziba bar God g…®foghamin fofozim ini. A mati mughuriar aghuim…®n m…®n otoz…®, am…®nim a b…®raz…® a tintinibar ghu. Bizir kam bagha k…® God m…®nabi.\f + \fr 2:14 \ft Grigh…®n akar otevitam kagh deragha m…®kemezir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 15 \x - \xo 2:15 \xt 1 Korin 1:18; 2 Korin 4:3\x*Guizbang…®ra, e mati pauran mughuriar aghuim zuim…®n m…®n, Krais a inigha ofan m…®n God gan…®ngi. Mughuriar kam, a God…®n Nguibam…®n zuir tuavim…®n zuir gumazamizibar tong…®n otiva zui. Egha uaghan hel…®n zuir tuavim…®n itir gumazamizibar tong…®n otiva zui.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 2:16 \xt Luk 2:34; Jon 9:39; 1 Pita 2:7-8\x*Egha hel…®n tuavim…®n zuir darasi, mughuriar kam barazima, an ovever mughuriam…®n m…®n zui. Egha me gamima, me ovei. Ez…® God…®n Nguibam…®n tuavim…®n zuir darasi, me mughuriar kam barazima, a mati ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim isir mughuriam. Egha a ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim me gan…®di. Tinara gavgavigh ingangarir kamagh garim damuam? Bar puvat…®.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 2:17 \xt 2 Korin 1:12; 4:2; 11:13; 1 Pita 4:11; 2 Pita 2:3\x*Ez…® e gumazamizir mabar m…®n amir puvat…®, me danganiba bar dagh aruava God…®n akam m…®g…®a, mati me dag…®aba bagha biziba amadi. God uab…® ingangarir kam e gan…®ngiz…® e ifarir puvat…®, e guizbang…®ra m…®gei. E Krais ko porogha, God…®n damazim…®n derav…®ram an akaba akuri. 
\c 3  
\s1 Aposelba Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Igiam…®n ingangarir gumazibar otifi 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 3:1 \xt Aposel 18:27; Rom 16:1; 2 Korin 5:12\x*E ti ian aghariba ap…®rt…®, ia suam, e gumazir aghuiba, kamagh…®n e ti m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kabagh ami? O e ti gumazir mabar m…®n e gumazibav k…®mt…®, me ia bagh ak…®nafariba osir ia m…®k…®m suam, e gumazir aghuiba? O e uarir akurvaghs…® ian azangs…®ght…®, ia en akurvaghamin ak…®nafarim osiram? Bar puvat…®!  
\v 2 \x - \xo 3:2 \xt 1 Korin 9:2\x*Ia uari, mati ak…®nafarir en gun gumazamizibav geim. Ez…® ak…®nafarir kam…®n osiziriba, da en navir averiabar aven iti. Eght…® gumazamiziba bar ak…®nafarir kam…®n gan…®va a d…®ponam.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 3:3 \xt Ua Me Ini 24:12; Jeremaia 31:33; Esekiel 11:19; 36:26; Hibru 8:10\x*Ia bar azenara iti, mati ak…®nafarir mam Krais an osiriz…® e a inigha ize. A f…®nf…®nir d…®pam…®n an osirizir puvat…®. A zurara ikiamin God…®n Duam…®n an osiri. Egha a dag…®ar ekiatam gis…®n an osirizir puvat…®. A gumazamizibar navir averiabar an osiri. 
\p  
\v 4 E fo, God ingangarir kam damuasava e am…®sefe. Ez…® Krais fofozir kam e gan…®ngi. Kamagh…®n, e akar kabar gun ia m…®gei.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 3:5 \xt Jon 15:5; 1 Korin 15:10; Filipai 2:13\x*Guizbang…®ra, e uari ingangarir kam damuan buraghburaki, egh e uari kamagh…®n m…®k…®man kogh suam, e uari bizibagh ami. Puvat…®, God uab…®ra gavgavim e gan…®dima, e ingangarir kam gami.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 3:6 \xt Jeremaia 31:31; Jon 6:63; Rom 7:6; 1 Korin 11:25; Galesia 3:10; Efesus 3:7; Kolosi 1:25; Hibru 8:6-8\x*Ez…® a uab…® e gamiz…®ma, e Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Igiar kam, e an ingangarir gumazibar otifi. Akar D…®k…®r…®zir kam, a bizir me ak…®nafarim…®n osirizir puvat…®zim, mati Moses Osirizir Arazir fom…®ram otoziba. Puvat…®. Kar God…®n Duam…®n bizim. Moses Osirizir Araziba gumazamizibagh amima me ovei. Ez…® God…®n Duam ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim me gan…®di. 
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 3:7 \xt Ua Me Ini 34:1; 34:28-30; God…®n Araziba 10:1; Rom 7:10\x*Ingangarir God amizim, a Moses Osirizir Arazibagh amiz…® da otifi. Ez…® tuavir kam…®n ovevem otos. Dughiar kam God dag…®am ab…®ghiz…®, osiziriba vaghvagha an otifi, ez…® God…®n angazangarim uaghan ize. Egha angazangarir kam Moses…®n guam gisiraz…® Israelia an guam…®n ganan buraghburaki. Ez…® g…®n angazangarir kam g…®fa.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 3:8 \xt Galesia 3:2; 3:5\x*Ingangarir God uan Duam gumazamizibar an…®ngasava amizim, a ingangarir Moses Osirizir Araziba an…®ngasava amizim, bar a gafira. Eght…® God…®n angazangarim ko gavgavim, ingangarir kam…®n ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 3:9 \xt God…®n Araziba 27:26; Rom 1:17; 3:21\x*Moses Osirizir Arazibar ingangarir kam, a en araziba tuis…®gh…®va e m…®k…®m suam, e ovengam. E fo, ingangarir kam God…®n angazangarim sara ize. Egh ingangarir kam God…®n angazangarim sara iz…®t…®, ingangarir gumazamizibar amut…® me God…®n damazim…®n deraghamim, a God…®n angazangarir bar ekiam sara iz…® mamagh…®ra ikiam.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 3:10 \xt Ua Me Ini 34:29\x*God…®n angazangarir ekiam ko gavgavim, ingangarir igiar an amizim ko ikia bar ekevegha mamagh…®ra iti. Egha angazangarir kam, God…®n angazangarir ingangarir ghurim ko itim, bar a gafira. Kamagh…®n, e dat…®r…®gh…®n gara n…®ghn…®si, ingangarir ghurim…®n angazangarim munge.  
\v 11 Ingangarir ghurir kam a zurara ikian kogham. Puvat…®, a mungegham. Egha a God…®n angazangarim sara ize. Kamagh…®n e fo, ingangarir igiar zurara ikiamim, a God…®n angazangarir bar ekiam sara iza mamagh…®ra iti. 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 3:12 \xt 2 Korin 7:4; Efesus 6:19\x*Ez…® e n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ikia bar fo, angazangarir kam iz…®va e bativ mamagh…®ra ikiam, ez…® e a bagha m…®zuai. Kamagh…®n, e atiati puvat…®gha azenara an gun m…®gei.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 3:13 \xt Ua Me Ini 34:33-35; Rom 10:4; Galesia 3:23\x*E Moses amiz…® mogh…®n amir puvat…®. An guam…®n angazangarim siragha mungemarima, a kamagh…®n aghua, Israelia an ganam. Kamagh…®n a inirav…®zim inigha uan guam avara.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 3:14 \xt Aisaia 6:10; Jon 12:40; Aposel 28:26-27; Rom 11:7-8; 11:25\x*Ez…® fom…®ra iza dat…®r…®gh…®n tuzir dughiam…®n, Israelian n…®ghn…®ziba bar p…®riz…®, me God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir Ghuribar gara, dar m…®ngariba deragha dagh fozir puvat…®. Egha mati Moses…®n guam avarazir inirav…®zim, men n…®ghn…®ziba avaraghav…®ra iti. Ez…® gumazitam o amizitam me avarazir inirav…®zir kam adangizir puvat…®. Krais uab…®ra, gumazim a g…®foght…®ma, God an inirav…®zir a dukuaghav itim adegham.  
\v 15 Guizbang…®ra, dughiaba bar me Moses Osirizir Arazibar bori, ez…® inirav…®zir kam ikia men n…®ghn…®ziba ap…®ra, iza dat…®r…®gh…®n oto.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 3:16 \xt Ua Me Ini 34:34; Aisaia 25:7; Rom 11:23; 11:26\x*Egh tina uan navim Ekiam bagh a giraght…®, God inirav…®zir an n…®ghn…®zim avarazim adegham.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 3:17 \xt Jon 8:32; 8:36; Rom 8:2; 1 Korin 15:45; 2 Korin 3:6; Galesia 5:1\x*K…® Ekiam m…®g…®a, kar k…® God…®n Duam m…®gei. Eght…® Ekiam…®n Duam gumazitam o amizitam…®n ik…®t…®, bizitam an suiragh a ik…®rarighan kogham. Bar puvat…®. A bar f…®righ…®r…®gh ikiam.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 3:18 \xt Ua Me Ini 16:7; 24:17; Rom 8:29; 1 Korin 13:12; 15:49; 1 Timoti 1:11\x*E bar mogh…®ra, bizitam en guaba avarazir puvat…®. Ez…® Ekiam…®n angazangarir ekiam e gisiraz…®ma, e ganganir guabar garim…®n m…®n otogha, God…®n angazangarim gumazamizibar akakasi. E zurara God…®n angazangarir kam isav…®ra iti, ez…® a bar en arazibagh ighav…®ra itima, e Ekiam…®n nedazim…®n m…®n otivav…®ra iti. Ekiam, a God…®n Duam, egha a bizir kabagh ami. 
\c 4  
\s1 Aposelba, me nguazir m…®nebar m…®n iti 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 4:1 \xt 2 Korin 3:6; 1 Timoti 1:13\x*God en apangkuvigha ingangarir kam e gan…®ngi. Ez…® kamagh…®n e ingangarir kam gamua am…®rvazir puvat…®.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 4:2 \xt 1 Korin 1:18; 2 Korin 2:17; 6:4; 6:7; 1 Tesalonika 2:3-5\x*E aghums…®zir arazir gumazamiziba mogava amiba, e ak…®rim ragha dagh asara. E ifavarir arazibagh amir puvat…®. Egha e God…®n akam g…®raz…®, a igharagha otozir puvat…®. E God…®n guiz…®n akam azenarama anekuri, eght…® gumazamiziba bar uan navir averiabar aven en araziba tuis…®gham. Egh me kamagh…®n fogham, e ingangarir bar aghuim God…®n damazim…®n a gami.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 4:3 \xt 1 Korin 1:18; 2 Korin 2:15; 2 Tesalonika 2:10\x*Ez…® tarazi Akar Aghuir e kurir kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghan kogh, mati inirav…®zim men n…®ghn…®zim avaraghav…®ra iti. Gumazamizir kaba, me hel…®n zuir tuavim…®n itibara.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 4:4 \xt Jon 1:18; 12:31; 12:45; 1 Korin 9:19; Efesus 2:2; Filipai 2:6; Kolosi 1:15; Hibru 1:3\x*Satan a nguazir kam…®n god…®n ifavarim, a gumazamizir kabar n…®ghn…®ziba m…®tatem dagh an…®ngiz…®ma, me n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim puvat…®. Ez…® kamagh…®n Krais…®n Akar Aghuim…®n angazangarim ko an apangkuvim men navir averiabar aven ghuava avenge. Kamagh…®n, me Krais deragha an garir puvat…®, a uab…® God…®n m…®rara itir nedazim. 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 4:5 \xt 1 Korin 1:9; 1:13; 1:19; 1:23; 2 Korin 1:24\x*E uari uan arazibar akam akurir puvat…®. E kamagh…®n akam akura ghaze, ‚ÄúKrais Iesus, a en Ekiam. Ez…® e Iesus…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am…®n g…®n ghua egha ian ingangarir gumazibar iti.‚Äù  
\v 6 \x - \xo 4:6 \xt Jenesis 1:3; Aisaia 9:2; 2 Korin 3:18; 1 Pita 2:9; 2 Pita 1:19\x*Fom…®ra God kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúM…®tatem…®n aven, angazangarim otogh siragham.‚Äù Ez…® God…®n kamnangran angazangarim iza en navir averiabar ikia e gamiz…®ma, e God…®n fofozir aghuiba iti. E Krais Iesus…®n guam…®n angazangarir kam…®n gara, egha e God…®n angazangarim ko an gavgavim g…®fo. 
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 4:7 \xt 1 Korin 2:5; 2 Korin 5:1; 12:9\x*E pura nguazir m…®ner k…®nir gavgaviba puvat…®zibar m…®n ami, ez…® bizir bar aghuir kam en aven iti. Bizir kam kamagh…®n en aka, gavgavir bar ekiar kam, a God…®n otifi, an en otivir puvat…®.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 4:8 \xt 2 Korin 1:8; 7:5\x*Ez…® dughiar mabar os…®mt…®zir av…®riba e bativigha, e d…®kab…®razir puvat…®. Ez…® bizir av…®riba en n…®ghn…®zibar iza e gamima e okam n…®ghn…®si, da en n…®ghn…®ziba bar da ap…®rizir puvat…®.  
\v 9 Gumazamizir av…®riba en apanibar itima, God e ataghizir puvat…®. Me e m…®sogha pazava e gamua, egha bar e gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 4:10 \xt Rom 8:17; 1 Korin 15:31; Filipai 3:10; 1 Pita 4:13\x*E kamaghsua, e uan ovengamin inivaf…®zir kaba, gumazamiziba Iesus…®n ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim men akaght…®ma, me dar ganam. Kamagh…®n e zurara uan ovengamin inivaf…®zibar, Iesus…®n ovevem men akakasi.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 4:11 \xt Rom 8:36; 1 Korin 15:31; 15:49\x*E kamagh…®n ifonge, e uan ovengamin inivaf…®zir kaba, e gumazamiziba Iesus…®n ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuim men akaght…®ma, me dar ganam. Kamagh…®n e angam…®ra ikia Iesus…®n ingangarim bang…®n, gumazamiziba e m…®sozima, e dughiar av…®ribar atam ariaghiri.  
\v 12 Kamagh…®n, e ghaze, ovevem e bativasa amuav…®ra iti, eght…® en arazir kam ia damut…®, ia ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim iniam. 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 4:13 \xt Onger Akaba 116:10; Rom 1:12; 2 Pita 1:1\x*Gumazir mam God…®n Duam…®n fofozim an itima, a God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n osiri, ‚ÄúK…® n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ikia, egha kamagh…®n k…® an gun m…®gei.‚Äù Kamagh…®ra, God…®n Duam en aven ingara e gamima, e uaghan n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ikia kamagh…®n an gun m…®gei.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 4:14 \xt Rom 8:11; 1 Korin 6:14\x*E kamagh…®n fo, God, Ekiam Iesus gamiz…®, a ua mozim…®n d…®kavigha ik…®r…®m…®rir aghuarim ini. A uaghan e damight…®, e Iesus ko ua d…®kavight…®, a bar e ko ia sara inigh mang…®t…®, e an borogh…®n ikiam.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 4:15 \xt 1 Korin 3:21; 2 Korin 1:3-6; Kolosi 1:24; 2 Timoti 2:10\x*Bizir e bativir kaba bar, da ia bang…®n e batifi. God kamaghsua, arazir kam…®n an apangkuvim gumazamizir av…®riba bativ mang…®v…®ra ikiam. Egh gumazamizir kaba a m…®nab…® mang…®v…®ra ik…®, an ziam fam. Kamagh…®n bizir kaba e batifi. 
\s1 Aposelba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Krais…®n ikia egha gavgavim ini 
\p  
\v 16 \x - \xo 4:16 \xt Rom 7:22; Efesus 3:16; Kolosi 3:10; 1 Pita 3:4\x*E ingangarir bar aghuir God amizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha, kamagh…®n an ingangarim damuasa am…®rvazir puvat…®. E fo, en inivaf…®zir azenan itiba, bar ikuvighasava amima, ez…® en navir averiabar aven, e zurara dughiabar gumazamizir bar igiabar m…®n otivav…®ra iti.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 4:17 \xt Matyu 5:12; Rom 8:17-18; 1 Pita 1:6\x*E fo, os…®mt…®ziba ko m…®zazir e dat…®r…®gh…®n ateriba, da os…®mt…®zir ekiaba puvat…®. Egh da dughiar otevimra ikiam. Egh da en akuraght…®, e dabirabir bar aghuim God…®n Nguibam…®n zurazurara a iniam. E fo, bizir aghuir e iniamin kaba, da bizir igharaziba bar dagh afiraght…®, os…®mt…®zir e dat…®r…®gh…®n aterir kaba, da pura bizibar m…®n otivigham.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 4:18 \xt Rom 8:24; 2 Korin 5:7; Kolosi 1:16; Hibru 11:1-3\x*E uan damazibar garir biziba, e dar gara dagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Bizir e uan damazibar ganan koghamiba, e m…®gh…®gha a dar gara dagh n…®ghn…®si. Bizir e uan damazibar gariba, da bar dughiar otevimra ikiam. Ez…® bizir aghuir e uan damazibar ganan koghamiba, da bar zurara ikiam. 
\c 5  
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 5:1 \xt 2 Korin 4:7; 2 Pita 1:13-14\x*E kamagh…®n fo, nguazim…®n purirpenir e dat…®r…®gh…®n aven itir kaba, da g…®n d…®p…®righir…®gh ikuvigham, kar en inivaf…®zim…®n ovevem. Eght…® dughiar kam God d…®penir igharazir aghuim e dan…®ngam, kar en inivaf…®zir igiam. D…®penir kam, gumazitam an ingarizir puvat…®, God uab…® an ingari. A God…®n Nguibam…®n ik…® zurazurara ik…®v…®ra ikiam.\f + \fr 5:1 \ft Purirpenir nguazim…®n itir kamnang, kar inivaf…®zir e nguazir kam…®n inizibar akar is…®n zuim. Ez…® d…®penir igharazir mam, kar e God…®n Nguibam…®n iniamin inivaf…®zir igharagha garir bar igiaba.\f* 
\v 2 \x - \xo 5:2 \xt Rom 8:23\x*E dat…®r…®gh…®n nguazim…®n d…®penir kam…®n ikia, egha navim bigha ara ikia uan d…®penir God…®n Nguibam…®n itim inigh, korotiam…®n m…®n e anerughasa bar ifonge.  
\v 3 E anerugh uan inivaf…®zim avaragh, egh bibiamra ikian kogham.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 5:4 \xt 1 Korin 15:53-54\x*E nguazim…®n purirpenim…®n aven ikiav…®ra ikia, os…®mt…®ziba atera navim bigha ara iti. Ez…® da e gamima e uan inivaf…®zir ghurir kam atagh…®raghasava amir puvat…®. E inivaf…®zir igiar aghuim a gis…®n aneghuasa ifonge, mati e korotiar igiam ghurim gis…®n anerught…®ma, anagapazagh ganganir bar aghuim damuam. Tuavir kam…®n en inivaf…®zir ovengamim, a ua ragh…®r…®gh, inivaf…®zir angam…®ra ik…®v…®ra ikiamim…®n otogham.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 5:5 \xt Rom 8:16; 8:23; 2 Korin 1:22; Efesus 1:14; 2:10\x*God uab…® e ak…®righa angam…®ra itir ik…®r…®m…®rir kam e gan…®ngi, egha uan Duam e gan…®ngi. God bizir bar aghuir maba e dan…®ngasa, egha faragha uan Duam e gan…®ngi. Ez…® e God…®n Duam inigha g…®vagha bar fo, e bizir aghuir igharaziba uaghan da iniam. 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 5:6 \xt Hibru 11:13-16\x*Kamagh…®n e bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha tuivigha gavgavighav…®ra iti. E fo, e inivaf…®zir kam sara ik…®va, Ekiam ko an Nguibam…®n ikian kogham.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 5:7 \xt Rom 8:24-25; 1 Korin 13:12; 2 Korin 4:18; Hibru 11:1\x*Bizir e gariba, e dagh n…®ghn…®gha, dar g…®n zuir puvat…®. E pura n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Ekiam…®n ikia, egha an g…®n zui.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 5:8 \xt Filipai 1:23\x*Ez…® k…® m…®kemegha g…®fa, e uan navibar suigha ikia, egha atiatir puvat…®. E inivaf…®zir ghurir kam ategh mang…® Ekiam ko ik…® an Nguibam…®n ikiasa bar ifonge. Eght…® an Nguibar a itim, guizbang…®ra en nguibam…®n m…®n ikiam.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 5:9 \xt Kolosi 1:10; 1 Tesalonika 4:1\x*Egha e nguibar manam…®n iti, an en nguibam, o God…®n Nguibam, e zurara kamagh…®n bar ifonge, e arazir aghuir Ekiam ifongezibar amuam.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 5:10 \xt Fofozir Gumazim 12:14; Rom 2:16; 14:10; Galesia 6:7; Kolosi 3:24-25; Akar Mogomem 22:12\x*Guizbang…®ra, e bar mogh…®ra Krais…®n kot…®n otivight…®, an en araziba tuis…®gham. Dughiar e nguazim…®n inivaf…®zim…®n aven itim, e arazir aghuibagh ami, o arazir kurabagh ami, eght…® kotiam…®n dughiam e bar vaghvagh uan arazir amizibar ivezim iniam. 
\s1 E gumazamizibar akurvaght…®, me God…®n namakabar otivam 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 5:11 \xt 2 Korin 4:2; Hibru 10:31; Jut 1:23\x*Egha e Ekiam…®n atiatiava an apengan iti. Kamagh…®n, gumazamiziba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ikiasa, e men n…®ghn…®ziba fa me gakaghori. God guizbang…®ra bar en n…®ghn…®ziba ko arazibagh fo. K…® uaghan kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, ia en araziba tuis…®gha fo, e ingangarir aghuim gami.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 5:12 \xt 2 Korin 1:14; 3:1\x*E ua m…®geir akar kam, e ian aghariba ap…®rt…®, ia en ziaba f…® suam, e gumazir aghuiba, e kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Ia fo, marazi pura gumazamizibar ziar ekiaba itiba bagha bar akongegha, men navim…®n aven otivir araziba bagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Ez…® e kamaghsua, ia gumazir kabar akaba ikarvaghamin fofozim ik…®. Bizir kam…®n e ia bagha osiri, eght…® ia en arazir aghuiba bagh bar akongegham.  
\v 13 Guizbang…®ra, marazi ghaze, en araziba ko en n…®ghn…®ziba ti gumazir onganibar m…®n iti. Puvat…®, kar e guizbang…®ra God…®n ingangarim gami. E n…®ghn…®zir aghuarim ik…®va, egh ian akurvaghs…® kamagh…®n damuam.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 5:14 \xt Rom 5:15\x*E deragha n…®ghn…®gha fo, gumazir mam bar e bagha areme. Ez…® tuavir kam mati, e bar mogh…®rama ovegha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n Krais e gifongezir arazim, en naviba fa e ab…®rima, e an ingangarim gami.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 5:15 \xt Rom 14:7-8; 1 Korin 6:19; Galesia 2:20; 1 Tesalonika 5:10; 1 Timoti 2:6; 1 Pita 4:2\x*Gumazir kam kamagh…®n ifonge, e gumazamizir angam…®ra itiba uarira uari bagh ikian kogham. E gumazir e bagha ovegha ua d…®kavizim baghv…®ra ikiam. Kamak…®n, a bar mogh…®ra e bagha ovenge. 
\p  
\v 16 \x - \xo 5:16 \xt Jon 6:63; Filipai 3:7-8; Kolosi 3:11\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e dat…®r…®gh…®n ua navir ghurim…®n arazim…®n g…®n ghua gumazamizibar araziba tuis…®zir puvat…®. Guizbang…®ra, e faragha navir ghurim…®n arazim…®n g…®n ghua Krais…®n araziba tuis…®ki. Egha dat…®r…®gh…®n ua kamagh…®n amir puvat…®.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 5:17 \xt Aisaia 43:18; Rom 8:1; 8:9-10; Galesia 5:6; 6:15; Efesus 2:15; Akar Mogomem 21:5\x*Gumazim o amizim Krais ko poroght…®, God a damight…®, a bar igiam…®n otogham. Eght…® bizir ghurim bar g…®vaght…®, bizir bar igiam otogham. 
\p  
\v 18 \x - \xo 5:18 \xt Rom 5:10; Efesus 2:16; Kolosi 1:20; 1 Jon 2:2\x*Bizir kaba bar, God dagh amima, da e batifi. E fom…®ra an apanibar m…®n iti, ez…® Krais…®n ingangarim…®n an e gamiz…®, e dat…®r…®gh…®n an namakabar otifi. Egha a uaghan, ingangarir kam e gan…®ngi, eght…® e an apanir igharazibar amight…®, me an namakabar otivam.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 5:19 \xt Rom 3:23-25; Kolosi 1:19-20\x*En m…®g…®r…®g…®am kamak…®n: God, Krais…®n ingangarim…®n tuavim…®n, a nguazim…®n itir gumazamiziba bar me gamima, me God…®n apanim gamir arazim atagh…®ragha an namakabar m…®n otifi. Egha men arazir kurar me amiziba, a ua dagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. Egha a ingangarir kam e gan…®ga ghaze, ia akam nan apanibav k…®night…®, me oregh nan namakabar otivigham.  
\v 20 \x - \xo 5:20 \xt 2 Korin 3:6; 6:1; Efesus 6:20\x*Kar e Krais…®n abuir gumazamizibar otivigha, mati God uab…® uan d…®mdiam ia gan…®ngiz…® mogh…®n, e akar kam ia m…®k…®ri. Kamagh…®n, e Krais…®n danganim isa, ia gakaghora ghaze, ia God…®n apanim gamir araziba ategh an namakabar otifigh.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 5:21 \xt Aisaia 53:6-12; Jon 8:46; Rom 5:19; 1 Korin 1:30; Galesia 3:13; Filipai 3:9; Hibru 4:14-15; 1 Pita 2:22-24; 1 Jon 3:5\x*Krais uab…® arazir kuratam gamizir puvat…®. Ez…® God kamaghsua, e Krais ko porogh, an gavgavim…®n e God…®n damazim…®n gumazamizir aghuibar otivam. Kamagh…®n, God en akurvaghasa en arazir kuraba bar Krais gis…®n da ar…®ki, ez…® Krais mati uaghan gumazir arazir kurabagh amir mam…®n m…®n oto. 
\c 6  
\s1 Aposelba uan ingangarim gamua os…®mt…®zir av…®riba ateri 
\p  
\v 1 God ko ingara pamten ia gakaghora ghaze, ia gumazamizir God…®n apangkuvim iniziba, ia aneteght…® a pura bizim…®n m…®n otivan mark…®.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 6:2 \xt Aisaia 49:8; Luk 4:19-21\x*God kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúDughiar k…® ian kuarkuvigha at…®zim, an otoz…®, k…® ian d…®mdiam barasi. Dughiar k…® ian akurvaghasa at…®zir kam, an otoz…®, k…® ian akura.‚Äù Ia oragh! K…® ian kuarkuvighamin dughiam dat…®r…®gh…®n otos. Ez…® uaghan k…® ian akurvaghamin dughiam dat…®r…®gh…®n otos! 
\p  
\v 3 \x - \xo 6:3 \xt Rom 14:13; 1 Korin 9:12; 10:32\x*Gumazitam o amizitam m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kuratam e amir ingangarim damuan e aghuagha, kamagh…®n en arazir e amiba bar, e gumazitam o amizitam gamiz…® a uan dagarim asegha ir…®zir puvat…®.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 6:4 \xt 2 Korin 4:2\x*E God…®n ingangarir gumazibar ikia, kamagh…®n zurara uan arazir aghuiba gumazamizibar akakasi. E men aghariba ap…®ra me m…®geima me kamagh…®n fo: Os…®mt…®zir e bativiba, ko bizir me bar pazava e gamiba, ko bizir e gas…®ghas…®ziba, e dar tuivigha gavgavighav…®ra iti.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 6:5 \xt Aposel 16:23; 2 Korin 11:23-27\x*Me e m…®sogha e isa kalabus…®n e ar…®si. Apanir av…®riba e akumakua n…®g…®nir dafam gamua en atari. Ez…® e puv…®ra ingara deragha akuir puvat…®ghava, m…®tiriabara iti.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 6:6 \xt 1 Timoti 4:12\x*E arazir God…®n damazim…®n zuezibagh amua, guiz…®n akam…®n fofozim…®n suira. E akamadariba ikarvagha bem…®ram atarir puvat…®. E arazir aghuibar gumazamizibagh ami. E God…®n Duam…®n gavgavim iti. E igharaz darazigh ifongezir arazim guizbang…®ram a gami. E arazir kabagh amua kamagh…®n ian aka, e guizbang…®ra God…®n ingangarir gumazamiziba.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 6:7 \xt 1 Korin 2:4; 2 Korin 10:4; Efesus 6:11-13; 2 Timoti 4:7\x*E guiz…®n akam akura, egha God…®n gavgavim…®n uan ingangarim gami. E God…®n arazir aghuim…®n suira, mati inogovim…®n bizibar m…®n, e uan agharir k…®riam ko guvim…®n dar suigha, God…®n ingangarim bagha m…®sosi. 
\p  
\v 8 Gumazamizir maba en ziaba fe. Ez…® igharaziba en ziabagh as…®ghas…®si. Ez…® marazi g…®rak…®rang…®n e m…®g…®a e gas…®ghas…®si, ez…® igharaziba en gun uan namakabav g…®a ghaze, e arazir aghuibagh ami. Gumazamizir maba ghaze, e gumazir ifariba. Kamagh…®n puvat…®, e gumazir guiz…®n akabav geiba.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 6:9 \xt Onger Akaba 118:18; 1 Korin 4:9; 2 Korin 4:2; 4:9-10\x*Marazi en gara, mati me e g…®fozir puvat…®. Ez…® guizbang…®ra, gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ram e g…®fos. Marazi en gara ghaze, dughiar av…®riba e atam ovei. Ez…® guizbang…®ra, e angam…®ra ikiav…®ra iti. Marazi en gara ghaze, God uam e ak…®rm…®ghasa m…®zazir ekiar kam e gan…®di. Ez…® guizbang…®ra, e aremezir puvat…®.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 6:10 \xt 2 Korin 7:4; Filipai 2:17; Kolosi 1:24\x*Marazi en gara ghaze, e bar oseme. Ez…® guizbang…®ra, e zurara bar akuegha iti. Marazi en gara ghaze, e onganarazibar m…®n iti. Ez…® guizbang…®ra, e gumazamizir av…®ribar akurvazima, me God…®n Duam…®n amodogh…®n, bizir aghuir av…®riba bar iz…®fa. Marazi en gara ghaze, e biziba puvat…®z…® mogh…®n pura iti. Ez…® guizbang…®ra, e God…®n Duam…®n amodogh…®n, e biziba bar av…®rasemegha iti. 
\p  
\v 11 Ia, Korin…®n itir Krais…®n adarasi, e azenara bigh…®v…®ra ia m…®k…®masa. E guizbang…®ra uan naviba kuighava da isa ia gan…®di.  
\v 12 E uan navibar kuaz…® pu. Puvat…®. E ia bagha bar ifonge. Ez…® ia uari uan navibar kumi. Ez…® navir vam…®ran itir arazir kam, en tong…®n itir puvat…®.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 6:13 \xt 1 Korin 4:14\x*K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n mati Afeziam uan boribav gei mogh…®n, k…® ia m…®gei. Ia arazir e amibar m…®n, uaghan uan naviba kuigh…®va da is…® e dan…®ngam. 
\s1 E God…®n D…®penim…®n m…®n iti 
\p  
\v 14 \x - \xo 6:14 \xt God…®n Araziba 7:2-3; 1 Korin 5:9; Efesus 5:7; 5:11\x*Krais…®n adarazir azenan itir gumazamiziba, men araziba bar ighara. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia me ko porogh me ko ingangaribar amuan mark…®. K…® ian azai, God…®n arazir aghuim ko arazir kuram ti manmagh…®n uaning ko porogh uaning ko ingaram? Eght…® angazangarim ko m…®tatem manmagh uaning inigh ikiam? Bar puvat…®gham.  
\v 15 Krais ko Satan, aning ti navir vam…®ran iti, o? O, gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim ititam, ko gumazamizir n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim puvat…®zitam, aning manmagh…®n n…®ghn…®zir vam…®ra ikiam? Bar puvat…®.  
\v 16 \x - \xo 6:16 \xt Ofa Gami 26:12; Esekiel 37:27; 1 Korin 3:16; 6:19\x*Manmaghsu, e God…®n D…®penim ko marvir guabar d…®peniba isafuragham? God fom…®ra kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® me ko ik…®, egh men tong…®n daruam. Eght…® me nan gumazamizibar m…®n ik…®t…®, k…® men God…®n ikiam.‚Äù Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia fo, e uari God…®n zurara itim…®n dabirabir D…®penim. 
\p  
\v 17-18 \x - \xo 6:17-18 \xt 2 Samuel 7:14; 1 Eghaghaniba 17:13; Aisaia 43:6; 52:11; Jeremaia 31:9; Esekiel 20:34; 2 Korin 7:1; Akar Mogomem 1:8; 18:4; 21:7\x*Ez…® Ekiam ua kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚Äú‚Äâ‚ÄòIa me ategh, mang…® danganir igharazitam…®n ik…®. Egh ia bar deraghv…®ra uari bagh gan, ia ua bizir God…®n damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®zitam uam an suighan mark…®. K…® uab…® ia inigh, ian Afeziam…®n m…®n ik…®t…®, ia nan boribar m…®n ikiam.‚Äô Ekiar Gavgavir Ekiam Itim kamagh…®n m…®gei.‚Äù 
\c 7  
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 7:1 \xt 2 Korin 6:17-18; 1 Jon 3:3\x*Nan namakar aghuiba, God…®n e bagha inabaz…® itir bizir kaba e da inigha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n, e inivaf…®zim ko duam gami aning m…®zezir biziba, bar da batuegh, God…®n damazim…®n bar zuegham. Egh e God…®n atiating an apengan ikiam. Egh uari is…® bar God danigh, egh God…®n arazir zuezim zuraram an g…®n mangam. 
\s1 Korinba navibagh iraz…®ma Pol bar akonge 
\p  
\v 2 \x - \xo 7:2 \xt Aposel 20:33; 2 Korin 12:17\x*Ia uan naviba kuigh…®va, da is…® e dan…®ng. E arazir kuratam…®n gumazitam o amizitam gamizir puvat…®. Egha e gumazitam o amizitam pazava a gamizir puvat…®. Egha e gumazitam o amizitam gifaragha an bizitam pura a inizir puvat…®.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 7:3 \xt 2 Korin 6:11-12\x*K…® akatam ia gasa m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam ia m…®geir puvat…®. Ia fo, k…® fom…®ra m…®keme, e uan naviba bar ia ganigha bar ia gifuegh…®v…®ra ikiam. Egh e ovengam, o e angam…®ra ik…®v…®ra ikiam, arazir kam kamagh…®ra ikiam.  
\v 4 K…® kamagh fogha bizitam modozir puvat…®. K…® bigh…®v…®ra ia m…®k…®mam, nan navim bar am…®ragh…®r…®z…®, k…® ia bagha bar akonge. Os…®mt…®ziba guizbang…®ra e batifi, ez…® da pura biziba. E ia g…®n…®ghn…®si, ez…® bizir kam e gamiz…®, en naviba ia bagha bar akueghav…®ra iti. 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 7:5 \xt 2 Korin 2:13\x*E ghua Masedonian itir dughiam, e avughsasa amuava avenge. Nguibar kam…®n os…®mt…®zir av…®rir maba zurara e isi. Gumazamiziba akabar, e uari batogha uariv gei. Ez…® atiatir n…®ghn…®ziba, en navir averiabar aven iti.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 7:6 \xt 2 Korin 1:3-4; 2:13\x*Gumazamizir os…®mt…®ziba men naviba ab…®nigha itiba, God men g…®rak…®rang…®n tuiva navir am…®rizim me gan…®di. Egha a Taitus amadaz…®ma, a uam e bagha izez…®ma, en navir averiaba bar dera.  
\v 7 Taitus ua izezir arazir kamra, God e gamiz…® en naviba derazir puvat…®. Ia faragha Taitus gamiz…® an navim ian dera, egha a ian arazir kam…®n gun e geghani. Ian arazir kam…®n God uaghan en navibagh amiz…® da dera. Taitus kamagh…®n e m…®g…®a ghaze, ia nan ganasa bar ifongegha, ararer kam ian navir averiabar iti. Egha ia na ko navir vam…®ran ikiasa bar puv…®ra n…®ghn…®si. Ez…® kamagh…®n k…® bar guizbang…®ra bar akonge. 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 7:8 \xt 2 Korin 2:4\x*K…® fo ak…®nafarir k…® ia bagha osirizim ia gamiz…®, ian naviba oseme. Ez…® k…® uab…® bizir kam m…®gh…®gha a g…®n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. K…® guizbang…®ra faragha bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha ian apangkufi, egha dat…®r…®gh…®n puvat…®. Ak…®nafarir k…® ia bagha osirizir kam ia gamiz…®, ia osemegha aghums…®ki. Ez…® arazir kam bar dughiar otevimram iti.  
\v 9 Ez…® k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n bar akonge. K…® fo, ia oseme, ez…® k…® bizir kam bagha bar akongezir puvat…®. K…® fo, ian os…®mt…®zim ko aghums…®zim ia gamiz…®, ia uan navibagh ira, ez…® k…® bizir kam bagha bar akonge. K…® fo, God uab…® ia gamiz…®, ian naviba osemegha aghums…®ki. Ez…® en m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kataba bar ian navibagh as…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 7:10 \xt 2 Samuel 12:13; Aghuzir Akaba 17:22; Matyu 26:75; 27:3-5; Hibru 12:16-17\x*E fo, God…®n otivir os…®mt…®ziba ko aghums…®zir araziba, da gumazamizibagh amima, me uan navibagh iragh…®rasi. Arazir kam…®n God uam en akura. Kamagh…®n, e arazir kam bagh uan navibagh is…®n n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribara amuan markiam. Ez…® nguazir kam…®n os…®mt…®ziba ko aghums…®zir araziba, da gumazamizibagh amima ovevem otifi.  
\v 11 Ia kamagh…®n deragh n…®ghn…®gh. God ia gan…®ngizir os…®mt…®zir kam, bizir bar aghuir igharagha garibar ia gami. Bizir kam…®n God ia gamiz…® ia uari, uari bagha uan os…®mt…®zim derav…®ra bigh…®v…®ra m…®k…®masa ia ifonge. Ez…® God ian naviba fez…®, ia gumazir arazir kuram gamizim…®n atari. Ez…® a ia gamiz…®, ia an atiatingi. Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n m…®gh…®gha e g…®n…®ghn…®gha, gumazir arazir kuram gamizim…®n arazim ak…®rasa pamten ingari. Arazir ia m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam ak…®rasava amiba, kamagh…®n akagha ghaze, ia God…®n damazim…®n os…®mt…®zitam itir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 12 K…® ak…®nafarir kam ia bagha an osira, egha arazir kuram gamizir gumazim g…®n…®ghn…®gha an osirizir puvat…®. Egha gumazir igharazir pazava a gamim, k…® uaghan a g…®n…®ghn…®ghizir pu. Bar puvat…®. K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, ian arazir aghuim azenim gir…®ght…®, ia God…®n damazim…®n deragh fogh suam, ia bar na gifonge. Bizir kam bagha k…® ak…®nafarir kam osiri. 
\p  
\v 13 Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ian arazir kam e gamiz…®, en navir averiaba am…®raghav…®ra iti. En naviba am…®ragh…®r…®gh iti, e bar akonge. Ia Taitus…®n akuragha an os…®mt…®ziba ag…®vaz…®, an navim am…®ra. Ez…® bizir kam…®n e guizbang…®ra bar akonge.  
\v 14 K…® faragha ian arazir aghuibar gun Taitus…®n m…®g…®a ian ziaba fe. Egha uan m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam…®n aghums…®zim inizir pu. Puvat…®. Akar e ian arazir aghuibar gun m…®kemeziba, da guizbang…®ra. Kamagh…®n dat…®r…®gh…®n Taitus fo, e ian ziaba fer m…®g…®r…®g…®aba, da bar guizbang…®ra.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 7:15 \xt 2 Korin 2:9\x*Taitus ia bagha izezir dughiam…®n, ia atiatia n…®gha, a inigha, bar an m…®g…®r…®g…®abar m…®rara ghue. A ian arazir kam g…®n…®ghn…®ghav…®ra ikia bar ian apangkuvigha navim ia bagha ikiav…®ra iti.  
\v 16 K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n bar fogha ghaze, ia arazir aghuibara damuam. Kamagh…®n k…® bar akonge. 
\c 8  
\ms1 Korinba, Judian itir Krais…®n adarazir akurvaghasa dag…®aba ar…®si 
\mr (Sapta 8--9) 
\s1 Krais…®n adarasi, Judian itir Krais…®n adarazi bagha dag…®aba ar…®si 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 8:1-4 \xt Rom 15:26\x*Nan adarasi, e kamagh…®n ia m…®k…®masa, God Masedonian Provins…®n itir siosba bar men apangkuvigha men akurvasi.  
\v 2 Os…®mt…®zir ekiam me batoz…®, dughiar kam…®n me biziba bar puvat…®. Ez…® God me gamiz…®, me bar akuegha, Krais…®n adarazigh n…®ghn…®gha, men akurvaghasa dag…®ar bar av…®riba ar…®zima da bar iz…®fa.  
\v 3 K…® derav…®ra kamagh…®n ia m…®k…®masa, me uari uan ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua dag…®ar kaba an…®ngi. Bizir me dan…®ngamin me itiba, me da an…®ga, dagh is…®n bar av…®riba an…®ngi.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 8:4 \xt 2 Korin 9:1-2\x*Me pamten e gaghora e m…®g…®a ghaze, e men amamangat…®ght…®, me God…®n apangkuvir arazim inigh, sios…®n igharaziba ko ingar…®va Judian itir God…®n gumazamizibar akurvagham.  
\v 5 E kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, me dag…®ataba an…®ngam. Ez…® men arazir aghuim, en n…®ghn…®zi mogh…®n, bar a gafira. Me uari isa God bar a gan…®ga, God ifongezir arazim…®n g…®n ghua uaghan uari isa bar e gan…®ngi. 
\p  
\v 6 Taitus faragha God…®n apangkuvir arazim…®n g…®n ghua ingangarir aghuir kam ian tong…®n a gami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e anemadi, eght…® a uamategh mang…®, uan ingangarir nam bar aneg…®vagham.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 8:7 \xt 1 Korin 1:5; 16:1-2; 2 Korin 9:8\x*Bizir ia amiba bar, da guizbang…®ra bar dera. Ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim God…®n ikia, derav…®ram an gun m…®gei. Egha ia fofozir ekiam ikia, God…®n ingangarim damuasa bar mogh…®ra ifonge. Egha ia uaghan e bagha bar ifonge. Kamagh…®ra, dat…®r…®gh…®n ia apangkuvir arazim…®n g…®n mang…®va a gis…®n arazir bar aghuir kam isafuragh ingangarir kam damu. 
\p  
\v 8 Ia nan akar kam…®n g…®rara mangasa k…® akar gavgavim ia gan…®dir puvat…®. K…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha ia m…®gei, gumazamizir igharaziba ingangarir kam damuasa naviba me d…®kafi. Eght…® ia damuamin arazir manatam…®n, k…® dar gan…®va da tuis…®gh deragh dagh fogham, ia igharaz darazigh ifongezir arazim a guizbang…®rama otifi, o puvat…®?  
\v 9 \x - \xo 8:9 \xt Matyu 8:20; Luk 9:58; Filipai 2:6-7\x*Ia fo, en Ekiam Krais Iesus, en apangkuvir arazim bar ekefe. A God…®n Nguibam…®n bizir aghuir bar av…®riba ikia, egha ia bang…®n nguazir kam…®n izegha onganarazim…®n m…®n iti. A ian akuraght…®, ia bizir av…®riba iniasa, kamagh…®n a biziba puvat…®zir gumazim…®n m…®n oto. 
\p  
\v 10 K…® dat…®r…®gh…®n ia dag…®aba ar…®zir ingangarir kam…®n uan n…®ghn…®zim ia dan…®ngasa. Ia azenir g…®vazim…®n ingangarir kam gamiz…® a d…®kafi. Egha ia ingangarir kam damuasa bar ifonge.  
\v 11 Egh ia dat…®r…®gh…®n ingangarir amir kam, ia gavgavigh aneg…®fagh! Ia faragha ingangarir kam damuamin ifongiam iti mogh…®n, ia zuam…®ra a damigh aneg…®fagh. Ia itir bizibar amodogh…®n, ia ingar mang…® otogh.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 8:12 \xt Mak 12:43; Luk 21:3\x*Gumazitam o amizitam bizibar an…®ngs…® bar ifueght…®, God da inis…® bar akuegham. God bizir gumazamiziba vaghvagha ikiava an…®dibagh n…®ghn…®gha, egha bizir me an…®diba isi. A gumazamizir biziba puvat…®zibagh n…®ghn…®gha men araziba tuis…®zir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 13-14 \x - \xo 8:13-14 \xt 2 Korin 9:12-13\x*K…® ia os…®mt…®zir ekiam atert…®, igharaz darazi derav…®ra ikiasa, k…® m…®geir puvat…®. K…® e arazir magh garibara e vaghvagh uarir amuasa, k…® ifonge. Ia dat…®r…®gh…®n dughiar kam…®n bizir av…®riba iti, ia biziba otevezir gumazamizibar akuragh. Eght…® g…®n ia bizibar oteveght…®, me bizir av…®rir me itibar ian akurvagham. Kamagh…®n, ia bar arazir vabara damuva, ia derav…®ra ikiam.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 8:15 \xt Ua Me Ini 16:18\x*Mati God…®n Ak…®nafarim m…®keme, ‚ÄúGumazamizir dagher av…®riba iniziba, men m…®neba izevezir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazamizir dagher av…®riba inizir puvat…®ziba, men dagheba otevezir puvat…®.‚Äù 
\s1 Pol gumaziba amangiz…®ma me Korin…®n ghue 
\p  
\v 16 God Taitus…®n navim fez…®ma, an e ko n…®ghn…®zir vam…®rama amua, uaghan ian akurvaghasa bar akonge. Kamagh…®n e God m…®nabi.  
\v 17 E ua ia bagh mangasava an azangs…®si, a mangasa bar ifonge. Egha a uaghan ingangarir kam damuasa bar ifonge. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a uab…® ifueghava, ia bagha ghu.  
\v 18 Ez…® e uaghan Krais…®n adarazir mav amadaz…®ma, a Taitus ko mar zui. Gumazir kam siosba bar dar Akar Aghuim akura, egha ziam iti.  
\v 19 Ez…® bizir kamra puvat…®. A en g…®n daru apangkuvim itir ingangarir kam damuasa, Siosba anem…®sevegha ghaze, an en akuragh dag…®aba ar…®gham. E kamaghsua, e ingangarir kam…®n Ekiam…®n ziam f…®t…®, gumazamiziba uaghan fogham, en naviba ingangarir kam damuasa d…®kavima e a gami. Bizir kamning bagha, e ingangarir kam gami.  
\v 20 Bizir ekiar gumazamiziba an…®ngiz…® e garim, tav a bagh akar kuratam e gasan e aghua. Kamagh…®n, e Krais…®n adarazir kav iniz…® an e ko izi.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 8:21 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 3:4; Rom 12:17; Filipai 4:8; 1 Pita 2:12\x*E arazir aghuibara damuasa. Egh e arazir aghuir kam God…®n damazimra a damuan aghua. Puvat…®, e uaghan gumazamizibar damazibar dar amuam. 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® e Krais…®n adarazir gumazir igharazir mam uaghan anemadaz…®ma, an aning ko zui. E dughiar av…®ribar ingangarir guar av…®riba a gan…®ga an garima, a gavgavigha deragha dagh ami. A bar fo, ia bar arazir aghuibara damuam. Kamagh…®n dat…®r…®gh…®n a ingangarir kam damuasa bar ifonge.\f + \fr 8:22 \ft E aveghbuar, Taitus ko Korin…®n mangasava amir kamning…®n ziamning, e deragha aning g…®fozir puvat…®. Pol ves 18 ko 20…®n mav…®n gun m…®keme. Egha igharazitav Pol ves 22…®n an gun m…®keme.\f* 
\v 23 Ia Taitus g…®fogha g…®fa, a nan roroam ko na ko ingarir gumazim, e ian akurvasi. Ez…® en aveghbuar kamning, ia kamagh…®n aning g…®fo, aning siosbar ingangarir gumazimning…®n ikia, aning…®n ingangarim…®n aning Krais…®n ziam fe.  
\v 24 \x - \xo 8:24 \xt 2 Korin 7:13-14; 8:1-7\x*Ia arazir bar aghuibar gumazir kabar amu. Eght…® ian arazir kam siosbar gumazamizibar akaght…®, me fogh suam, ia guizbang…®ra igharaz darazigh ifonge. Egh me fogham, e faragha me m…®g…®a ian ziam fe, ez…® akar kam, a guizbang…®ra, e pura m…®geir puvat…®. 
\c 9  
\s1 Korinba dag…®aba God…®n gumazamizibar akurvaghs…® dar an…®ngam 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 9:1 \xt 2 Korin 8:1-7\x*Ia dag…®ar e God…®n gumazamizir Judian itibar akurvaghasa ar…®gh…®zibagh fogha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® akar ruaritam bizir kam bagh an osiran kogham.  
\v 2 K…® fogha g…®fa, ia igharaz darazir akurvaghasa ian naviba d…®kavigha g…®fa. Ez…® k…® zurara ian ziaba Masedonian gumazamizibar damazibar da fe. K…® kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúAzenir g…®vazim Akaiaba ingangarir kam damuasa biziba ak…®righa g…®fa.‚Äù Egha me orazi ia dag…®aba an…®ngasa bar ifonge, ez…® bizir kam Masedonian av…®ribar naviba fema me uaghan dag…®abar an…®ngasa.  
\v 3 Ez…® nan m…®g…®r…®g…®ar k…® ian ziaba fer kaba, pura bizim…®n m…®n otivan, k…® kamagh…®n aghua. K…® kamagh…®n ifonge, ia dag…®aba arigh…®va, egh k…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, ia da me dan…®ngs…®v…®ra ia gan ik…®. K…® bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha, aveghbuar kaba amangiz…®, me ia bagha izi.  
\v 4 K…® guizbang…®ra n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim kamagh…®n iti, ia dag…®abar an…®ngasa da arigha m…®zuai iti. Nan n…®ghn…®zim Masedonian gumazitaba na ko iz…® gant…®, ia dag…®aba arighan koght…®, k…® bizir kam…®n aghums…®zim inigham. Eght…® ia uaghan bar aghums…®gham.  
\v 5 Kamagh…®n k…® ghaze, k…® gumazir kaba amadaght…® me faragh iz…® ian gan…®va, ian akuragh dag…®ar ia dan…®ngasa akam ak…®riziba, dar ak…®righ da amadaght…® da mangam. Eght…® k…® izamin dughiam…®n, gumaziba ian gant…®, ia bar akuegh dag…®ar kabar an…®ngam. Egh me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan kogham, e men dag…®aba ok…®masa me gifari. Puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 6 \x - \xo 9:6 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 11:24; 22:9; Rom 12:8; Galesia 6:7-9\x*Ia deragh bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh. Gumazim dagher bofera oparigh, a bar bofera iniam. Eght…® gumazim dagher av…®riba oparigh, a dagher bar av…®riba iniam.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 9:7 \xt God…®n Araziba 15:7; Aghuzir Akaba 11:25; Rom 12:8\x*Kamagh amiz…®, ia bar vaghvagh derav…®ra faragh n…®ghnigh, egh bizir ia an…®ngasa ifongezim faragha a g…®fogh. Gumazitam o amizitam uan bizitam an…®ngs…® osemegh suam, me bizibara an…®ngasa puv…®ram e gaghora e ab…®ri. Gumazamizir bar akuegha uan ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua biziba an…®diba, God bar me gifonge.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 9:8 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 28:27; Filipai 4:19\x*God bizir aghuir guar av…®riba ia dan…®ngamin gavgavim iti, eght…® ia bizir aghuir bar av…®riba ikiam. Egh ia zurazurara biziba bar iz…®vagham. Eght…® ia ingangarir aghuiba bar dar amus…®, bizir bar av…®riba ia bagh iz…®vagh ikiam.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 9:9 \xt Onger Akaba 112:9\x*God…®n Ak…®nafarim arazir kam m…®g…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazamizir bizir av…®riba isa onganarazibagh an…®diba, me mati gumazamiziba dagher ov…®ziba oparasa pura tintinibar nguazim m…®k…®ri. Ez…® men arazir aghuir kam g…®vaghan kogham, a ik…®v…®ra ikiam.‚Äù  
\v 10 \x - \xo 9:10 \xt Aisaia 55:10; Hosea 10:12; Matyu 6:1\x*God dagher ov…®ziba gumazamizibagh an…®dima me uan azenibar da opari. Egha dagher guar bar av…®riba isa gumazamiziba bar me gan…®dima, me da api. Kamagh…®ra God biziba uaghan ia dan…®ngt…®, ia bar iz…®vagham. Kamagh…®ra ia God…®n gumazamizir igharaziba men akurvagham. Eght…® ian arazir aghuiba otiv mang…®v…®ra ik…®, mati gumazim dagher ov…®ziba opariz…® dar dagheba otiva ghuav…®ra iti.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 9:11 \xt 2 Korin 1:11; 4:15\x*God zurara bizir bar av…®riba ia dan…®ngt…®, ia bizir av…®riba igharaz darazi dan…®ngamin tuavim ikiam. Eght…® en ingangarim…®n, ia me dan…®ngamin bizir kaba, me damight…®, me God bar a m…®nabagham. 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 9:12 \xt 2 Korin 8:14\x*Kamagh amiz…®, ingangarir ia amir kam God…®n gumazamizibar akuraght…®, me uam bizibar oteveghan kogham. Egh uaghan ingangarir kam gumazamizibar amight…®, me God bar a m…®nabagham.  
\v 13 Ingangarir ia amua men akurvazir kam, a ian arazir aghuim bar azenaram anekagham. Eght…® me fogh suam, ia Krais…®n Akar Aghuim guiz…®n a inigha, deraghav…®ra an akam…®n g…®n zui. Eght…® me bizir av…®rir ia me gan…®ngiziba, ko bizir ia gumazamizir igharazibagh an…®ngiziba uaghan dar gan, egh God…®n ziam fam.  
\v 14 Egh me kamagh…®n fogham, God…®n apangkuvim guizbang…®ra bar ia giz…®fa. Kamagh…®n, me bar ia gifuegh, God bar derav…®ra ia damus…®, me ia bagh God…®n azangs…®gham.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 9:15 \xt Jems 1:17\x*Bizir aghuir God e gan…®ngizim, a guizbang…®ra bar ekefe, ez…® e a m…®k…®mamin akabagh asa. E pura bizir ekiar kam bagh God m…®namam! 
\c 10  
\ms1 Gumazir maba akar kuram…®n Pol m…®kemegha, Korinbagh amiz…®,  // me Pol…®n oseme.  // Ez…® Pol men n…®ghn…®ziba ua dar k…®ri 
\mr (Sapta 10--13) 
\s1 Pol gumazir an ingangarim ab…®nasava amibar akaba ikarvasi 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 10:1 \xt 1 Korin 2:3\x*Gumazamizir maba kamagh…®n akam na gasa na m…®g…®a ghaze, Pol e ko ikia bar uab…® ab…®ragha iti. Egha a saghon ikia akar bar gavgaviba e gan…®di. Ez…® k…® Pol, nan ifongiam kamak…®n, ia uari am…®ragha itir arazim, ko igharazibar asughasugha deragha me gamir arazir Krais amizim g…®n…®ghn…®gh. Egh k…® Krais…®n arazir kabar g…®n ghua, akar k…® m…®geiba ia deragh dagh n…®ghn…®ghasa k…® ian azangs…®si.\f + \fr 10:1 \ft Sapta 10--13…®n itir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba, da 2 Korin…®n itir saptan igharaziba, mong dar m…®rara ghuezir puvat…®. Pol sapta 9…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, a Korinbar araziba bagha bar ifonge. Egha ua sapta 10…®n bar akar gavgavibar me gami. Bizir kam…®n fofozir gumazir maba kamagh n…®ghn…®si, Sapta 10--13…®n ak…®nafarir Pol dughiar igharazim…®n osirizim…®n aven iti. Ez…® g…®n mogh…®ra gumaziba uaghara aning isafura.\f* 
\v 2 \x - \xo 10:2 \xt 1 Korin 4:21\x*K…® kamagh…®n ia gaghora ia m…®k…®masa, ia derav…®ra ganigh fogh, k…® iz…® ia ko ik…®va uam akar bar gavgavitam ia m…®k…®man maraghe. Gumazir e m…®g…®a ghaze, e nguazim…®n bizibar g…®n zuiba, k…® akar gavgavim me m…®k…®mamin gavgavim iti.  
\v 3 Guizbang…®ra e nguazir kam…®n ikia, nguazir kam…®n itir gumazamizibar m…®n m…®sozir puvat…®.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 10:4 \xt 1 Korin 2:5; Efesus 6:13-17; 1 Tesalonika 5:8; 1 Timoti 1:18\x*Inogovir bizir e suighiziba, da nguazim…®n inogovir biziba pu. Bar puvat…®. Bizir kaba, God…®n gavgavim dar iti. Eght…® e dar suigh…®va apanibar d…®v…®nir gavgavim ab…®gh…®rar…®gham.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 10:5 \xt 1 Korin 1:19; 3:19\x*Egha e ifavarir akaba, ko n…®ghn…®zir guar av…®riba d…®kab…®ri. N…®ghn…®zir kaba, gumazamiziba God…®n fofozim iniasava amima, da men tuaviba ap…®ri. Ez…® e gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®ziba ikiaghar…®si, mati me gumazir kuram isa kalabus gat…®. Egh e men n…®ghn…®zibar amight…®, men n…®ghn…®ziba Krais…®n akam…®n g…®rara mangam.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 10:6 \xt 2 Korin 2:9\x*Ez…® e iarara m…®zuai. Ia en akaba bar dar g…®n mang…®t…®, e gumazamizir akaba batoziba, m…®zazim me dan…®ngam. 
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 10:7 \xt 1 Korin 3:23; 14:37; 2 Korin 5:12; 1 Jon 4:6\x*Ia bar derav…®ra bizir azenan itir ia gariba tuis…®gh. Egh gumazitam o amizitam uab…®ra uab…® m…®k…®m suam, a guizbang…®ra Krais…®n anav, a bar derav…®ra n…®ghnigh kamagh…®n fogh, e uaghan an m…®rara Krais…®n adarasi.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 10:8 \xt 2 Korin 12:6; 13:10\x*Ekiam ingangarir kam damuasa gavgavim e gan…®ngi. Egha, e ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba fasa, a ifonge. Egha e ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgavibagh as…®ghas…®ghan a bar aghua. Kamagh amiz…®, k…® ingangarir e amir kam bagh bar akuegh, e uan ziaba tong ada fegh, akar m…®kemezir kam…®n aghums…®ghan kogham.  
\v 9 Ia kamagh…®n na g…®n…®ghn…®ghan k…® aghua, k…® gumazir ak…®nafariba ia bagha da osira atiatim ia gan…®dim.  
\v 10 Gumazamizir maba guizbang…®ra kamagh…®n na m…®gei, Pol…®n ak…®nafariba akar gavgavir igharagha gariba dar iti. Ez…® a uab…® iza e ko m…®geir dughiaba, e an garima a gavgaviba puvat…®. Egha akam akurir arazim bar deragha a g…®fozir puvat…®.  
\v 11 \x - \xo 10:11 \xt 2 Korin 7:14; 12:6; 13:2; 13:10\x*Gumazamizir m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kabagh amiba, me bar deragh n…®ghnigh kamagh…®n fogh, arazir e iza ia ko ikia amiba, da mati arazir e saghon ikia ia bagha Ak…®nafarim osiriz…® mogh…®n, da dar m…®rara ghu. 
\p  
\v 12 \x - \xo 10:12 \xt 2 Korin 3:1; 5:12\x*E kamagh m…®k…®man kogh, uari tuis…®gh suam, e gumazamizir uarira uan ziaba feba ko, e uaghara ghue. Egh e kamagh…®n m…®k…®man kogham, en araziba men araziba ko magh ghu. Puvat…®, gumazamizir kaba uari uan araziba tuis…®si. Egha gumazir mam uan arazim igharazitav…®n arazim koma a tuis…®si. Gumazamizir kamagh…®n amiba, me fofozir aghuiba bar puvat…®.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 10:13 \xt Rom 12:3\x*E uari uarigh is…®vagh p…®n mavanangan aghua, eght…® en ziaba bar p…®n mar ikiam. Puvat…®, e ingangarir God e bagha inabazim damuasa, God e bagha abaraz…® mogh…®n, e uan araziba tuis…®ghasa. Ez…® ingangarir God e gan…®ngizir kam…®n ababanim, ia Korinba uaghan aven iti.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 10:14 \xt 1 Korin 3:5; 3:10; 4:15; 9:1\x*Ez…® ingangarir God e gan…®ngizir kam…®n ababanim, a uaghan ia avara. Kamagh…®n, dughiar e akam ia m…®k…®rim, e ababanir kam…®n ikiavk…®nizir puvat…®. Erara bar faraghav…®ra Korin…®n iza Krais…®n Akar Aghuir kam ia bagha a inigha ize.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 10:15 \xt Rom 15:20\x*E uan ababanim gafirazir puvat…®gha, gumazamizir igharaziba amizir ingangarim g…®n…®ghn…®gha, uan ziaba fer puvat…®. Bar puvat…®: E ingangarir God e gan…®ngizim guizbang…®rama a damuasa ifonge. Eght…® ian n…®ghn…®zir gavgaviba gavgavight…®, en ingangarir kam ian tong…®n bar ekevegham.  
\v 16 Eght…® e Akar Aghuim inigh ian g…®rak…®rang…®n itir kantribar mangam. E nguibar gumazamiziba ingangarim gamigha g…®vazibar mangan aghua. Egha e gumazamizir igharaziba amigha g…®vazir ingangarim bagh pura uan ziaba fan aghua.\f + \fr 10:16 \ft Pol, Korin…®n g…®rak…®rang…®n itir kantribav gei. Kar, a ti Korin…®n aruem uaghiri nagh…®n itir kantribagh n…®ghn…®si. A ti Rom ko Spen aning…®n m…®gei.\f* 
\v 17 \x - \xo 10:17 \xt Jeremaia 9:24; 1 Korin 1:31\x*God…®n Ak…®nafarim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúTina bar akongeghs…®, an Ekiam amizir arazibagh n…®ghn…®gh, a bagh bar akongegh.‚Äù  
\v 18 \x - \xo 10:18 \xt Aghuzir Akaba 27:2; Rom 2:29; 1 Korin 4:4-5\x*E fo, gumazamiziba bar akuegha uarira uan ziaba fe, gumazamizir kaba God…®n damazim…®n ziaba pu. Bar puvat…®. Eght…® Ekiam gumazamizibar ziaba f…®t…®, gumazamizir kaba guizbang…®ra ziaba iti. 
\c 11  
\s1 Pol…®n arazim Aposel…®n ifavaribar arazibar m…®rara zuir puvat…® 
\p  
\v 1 Ia nan amamangat…®ght…®, k…® onganiz…® mogh…®n tong m…®kemeka. Ia nan amamangat…®gham, o?  
\v 2 \x - \xo 11:2 \xt Hosea 2:19-20; 1 Korin 4:15; Galesia 4:17-18; Efesus 5:26-27; Kolosi 1:28\x*God gumazamiziba anar…®ram apengan ikiasava a ifonge. Ez…® kamagh…®ra, ia Kraisra g…®n mangasa, k…® uaghan ifonge. Ia Krais…®n adarazir m…®rara ikiasa k…® ia m…®sefe, mati amizir igiar bar zuezim k…® a inigh mang…® par a ko poroghamim dan…®ngam.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 11:3 \xt Jenesis 3:1-5; 3:13; Jon 8:44; Hibru 13:9; 2 Pita 3:17\x*Ia kuruzim fom…®ra Iv gifarazim…®n eghaghanim g…®n…®ghn…®gh. K…® kamagh…®n atiati, bizir Iv batozir kam uaghan ia batogham. Gumazir kuram ia gifaraghan maraghe, eght…® ia ua Krais baghav…®ra itir guiz…®n arazim ategham.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 11:4 \xt Galesia 1:7-9\x*K…® fo, gumazamizir maba ia bagha iza Iesus…®n igharazim…®n akam ia m…®k…®ri. Kar Iesus…®n e akam ia m…®k…®nizim, puvat…®. Ez…® arazir kam…®n ia duar igharagha garim ini. Kar ia faragha inizir God…®n Duam puvat…®. Ia akar aghuir igharazim ini. Kar Akar Aghuir ia faragha inizim puvat…®. K…® fo, me ian tong…®n arazir kam gamiz…®, ia pura uari isa men m…®g…®r…®g…®abar g…®n mangasava ami. 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 11:5 \xt 1 Korin 15:10; 2 Korin 12:11; Galesia 2:6\x*Ia orakigh! K…® ghaze, ian gumazir ‚ÄúAposel…®n Ekiabar,‚Äù ar…®ziba, me na gafiraz…® k…® men apengan itir pu. Bar puvat…®.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 11:6 \xt 1 Korin 1:17; 2:1; 2:13; 2 Korin 4:2; 10:10; Efesus 3:4\x*Guizbang…®ra, k…® akam akurir arazim mong deragha a g…®fozir puvat…®. Ez…® nan fofozim otevezir puvat…®. Arazir e zurarama amiba, e uan fofozim gumazamiziba bar men akakazima, ia derav…®ra dar gani. 
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 11:7 \xt 1 Korin 9:12; 9:18\x*Ia fo, k…® God…®n Akar Aghuim ia m…®k…®ni, egha ingangarir kam…®n ivezitam inizir puvat…®. Arazir kam…®n, k…® ia fasa, egha uab…®ra uab…® ab…®ragha iti. Manmagh…®n ami, arazir k…® amir kam, k…® ti arazir kuram gami, o? Puvat…®.  
\v 8 K…® ian tong…®n ingangarim gamima, sios…®n igharaziba nan akuraz…®, k…® me da dag…®aba ini. Arazir kam mati, k…® men biziba okemegha ian akura.  
\v 9 \x - \xo 11:9 \xt 2 Korin 12:13; Filipai 4:15-18; 1 Tesalonika 2:9\x*Dughiar k…® ia ko itim…®n, k…® dag…®abar otevegha, da bagha ian tav…®n azangs…®zir pu. Puvat…®, Krais…®n marazi Masedonian Provins…®n ikegha iza bizir k…® otevegha ifongeziba, me bar dar nan akura. K…® kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®si, k…® os…®mt…®zim ia dan…®ngan aghuagha n…®ghn…®zir kam…®n suiraghav…®ra iti.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 11:10 \xt 1 Korin 9:15\x*K…® fo, k…® uan arazir kam bagha uan ziam fe. Ez…® Krais…®n guiz…®n akam na ko itima k…® guiz…®n kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, Akaian Provins…®n nguibaba bar, dar gumazitam o amizitam k…® uan ziam fer arazir kam bagh, nan tuavim ap…®righan kogham.  
\v 11 K…® tizim bagh kamagh…®n damuam? K…® ti ia gifongezir pu? Puvat…®, God bar fo, k…® bar ia gifonge. 
\p  
\v 12 Gumazamizir maba uarira uan ziaba fasa tuaviba buria gumazamizibar damazibar e ko magh otivasava ami. Ez…® k…® men tuavir kam ap…®rasava ami. K…® kamagh…®ra ingar mamagh…®ra ikiam. 
\p  
\v 13 \x - \xo 11:13 \xt Rom 16:18; 2 Korin 2:17; Galesia 1:7; Filipai 3:2; 2 Pita 2:1; Akar Mogomem 2:2\x*Gumazamizir kaba me aposel…®n ifavariba ko ingarir gumazir ifavariba. Me gumazibagh ifar uan araziba otavk…®nt…® gumazamiziba men gan suam, me guizbang…®ra Krais…®n aposelbar iti.  
\v 14 \x - \xo 11:14 \xt Galesia 1:8\x*Eght…® ia men arazir kurabar gan, d…®gavir kuram damuan mark…®. E fo, Satan uab…® uan arazim oteghavk…®nigha, angazangarim…®n ensel…®n m…®n oto.  
\v 15 \x - \xo 11:15 \xt 2 Korin 3:9; Filipai 3:19\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Satan…®n ingangarir gumazamiziba uaghan uan araziba otevk…®nigh, God…®n arazir aghuim…®n ingangarir gumazamizibar m…®raram otoght…®, e kamagh…®n ganigh d…®gavir kuram damuan kogham. Me g…®n me amir arazir kurar kam baghv…®ra ivezim guizbang…®ram a iniam. 
\s1 Pol Aposel…®n ingangarim gamir dughiam…®n, an os…®mt…®zir bar av…®riba ateri 
\p  
\v 16 \x - \xo 11:16 \xt 2 Korin 12:6\x*K…® faragha m…®kemegha g…®vagha dat…®r…®gh…®n ua m…®gei, ia nan m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam baragh kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®, k…® gumazir onganim. Egha ia gumazir onganim…®n na ar…®si, a uaghan dera. Egh ia nan amamangat…®ght…®ma, k…® uan ziam tong a feka.  
\v 17 K…® Ekiam…®n ifongiam…®n g…®n ghua m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam gamir puvat…®. K…® gumazir onganim…®n m…®n m…®g…®a, uab…® uan ziam fe.  
\v 18 Gumazamizir av…®riba nguazim…®n bizibar g…®n ghuava, uari uan ziaba fe. Eght…® k…® uaghan arazir kam…®n g…®n mang…®va uan ziam fam. 
\p  
